# 🛡️ AtlasCare — Agentic AI for Customer Contact

**Project AtlasCare** is a production-grade, LangGraph-based agentic AI system built for Acme Retail Co. It autonomously handles Tier-1 customer support interactions via a modern React chat UI, backed by a FastAPI server. The system supports SSO login via Auth0, dual personas (User & Admin), a live operational metrics dashboard, and a full observability/audit trail on every interaction.

Technology Stack
